# Component templates (from `components.json`)

This document summarizes **recurring shapes** used across the **310** component files listed in [`.agents/file-lists/components.json`](../file-lists/components.json). Use it as a quick reference when adding or refactoring UI. **Prefer `pnpm scaffold component <Name>`** (see **`rules-bundle-core.mdc`** + **`.agents/scaffold/README.md`**, **`.agents/scaffold/README.md`**) for new files instead of copying this by hand. Authoritative rules remain in **`rules-typescript-clean-code.mdc`**, **`rules-folder-organization.mdc`**, **`rules-bundle-react.mdc`**, and **`rules-bundle-react.mdc`**.

## Inventory snapshot (generated metadata)

| Fact | Typical value |
| --- | --- |
| Extensions | `.tsx` only in this list |
| Path depth (segments) | min 4, median 8, max 14 under `app/` |
| Top roots | `app/pages` (~61%), `app/components` (~22%), `app/features` (~16%) |
| Largest page area | `app/pages/Result/...` (~51% of listed files) |
| Co-located folder name = file stem | ~43% use `ComponentName/ComponentName.tsx` |

